(March 14, 1955.) Robert L. Bradford, Appellant, v. Nicholas M. Pette, Respondent.

Motion to dismiss appeals granted, without costs, and appeals dismissed, without costs. Present — MacCrate, Acting P. J., Schmidt, Beldock, Murphy and Ughetta, JJ. [204 Misc. 308.] [See post, p. 1193.]
